title: Set page break for table inside list group header will cause data display error.
OB: The table inside the list group header does not have a proper page break setting, leading to a data display error.
EB: When a page break is set for the table inside the list group header, the data should be displayed correctly on each page in the Web Viewer.
SR: Ensure that the table inside the list group header has a proper page break setting to prevent data display errors.
